	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><i>The Authority</i> (comics)</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">&#160;&#160;(Redirected from <a href="/w/index.php?title=Jenny_Quantum&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="Jenny Quantum">Jenny Quantum</a>)</span></div>
