<p><i>The Authority</i> #21 was also collected in <i><a href="/wiki/Monarchy_(comic_book)" class="mw-redirect" title="Monarchy (comic book)">The Monarchy</a>: Bullets Over Babylon</i> trade (<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1-56389-859-4" title="Special:BookSources/1-56389-859-4">1-56389-859-4</a>) since it was the starting point for <i>The Monarchy</i> series.
