<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Awards">Awards</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Authority_(comics)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Awards">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>The series was nominated for "Outstanding Comic Book" in the <a href="/wiki/14th_GLAAD_Media_Awards#Print" title="14th GLAAD Media Awards">14th</a> and <a href="/wiki/15th_GLAAD_Media_Awards#Print" title="15th GLAAD Media Awards">15th GLAAD Media Awards</a>.<sup class="noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style="white-space:nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources. (December 2015)">citation needed</span></a></i>&#93;</sup>
</p>
